The Ukrainians I have spoken with are devastated. I have never seen or felt anything like this. Terror. 

Please do what you can to support our Ukrainian brothers and sisters.

I went to the Hungary-Ukraine border today.  

The border towns I saw are some of the poorest places Iâ€™ve been to in EU with no shelter/infrastructure to receive refugees (pic).

Many Ukrainians on foot, with no plan and 100km to traverse before any possible shelter.

-Best places to cross the border
